Discover and catalog all your data
Discover and inventory all your data assets across your cloud infrastructures, even the ones you didn't know existed. Get a real-time catalog that continuously keeps track of your evergrowing data.

Teleskope supports structured and unstructured data stores, across AWS, GCP and Snowflake.
Classify and understand its risks
Get a complete picture of the security and privacy posture of your data. Understand the risks around how your data is stored, and who has access to it. Classify the content of each data asset, and pinpoint what types of personal and sensitive data are stored within them. Implement custom detection rules to identify data elements unique to you.Teleskope identifies over 75+ data elements, including personal, payments, healthcare, and sensitive data.
Automate and protect it



Customize your own security and privacy protocols on top of Teleskope's insights. Integrate Teleskope's APIs into any of your existing workflows and tools, and enforce data security from within at the earliest stages of the development lifecycle.

Automate manual assessments

Eliminate alert fatigue

Marketing
These items are used to deliver advertising that is more relevant to you and your interests. Personalization
These items allow the website to remember choices you make (such as your user name, language, or the region you are in) and provide enhanced, more personal features. For example, a website may provide you with local weather reports or traffic news by storing data about your current location.
Analytics
These items help the website operator understand how its website performs, how visitors interact with the site, and whether there may be technical issues. This storage type usually doesnt collect information that identifies a visitor.
